(32, 'Bauer Nexus ADV Hockey Stick', '1column', 'Bauer Nexus ADV Senior Griptac Hockey Stick | Sports Zone Canada, Bauer Nexus ADV Intermediate Griptac Hockey Stick, Bauer Nexus ADV Junior Griptac Hockey Stick, Nexus ADV 2020 Stick, New Bauer Nexus Stick', 'Find the Brand new, 2020 Bauer Nexus ADV Griptac Hockey Stick. The Nexus ADV is packed with cutting edge technology to provide elite players with enhanced power and control, while remaining the lightest Nexus stick that\'s ever been created. This stick features new 5-Sided Shaft Geometry, Bauer\'s SlingTech Blade, Advanced Carbon Layering + ER Spine Tech, and the ADV Sonic Shaft Taper. Free Shipping*.\r\n', 'bauer-nexus-adv-stick', 'Bauer Nexus ADV Griptac Hockey Stick 2020', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/team-sports-hockey/composite-sticks/senior-stick/bauer-nexus-adv-gr-stk-sr-142613.html\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"274\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/NexusADVStick/Nexus_ADV_Senior.jpg\"}}\" width=\"204\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/team-sports-hockey/composite-sticks/intermediate-stick/bauer-nexus-adv-gr-stk-int-142603.html\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"271\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/NexusADVStick/Nexus_ADV_Intermediate.jpg\"}}\" width=\"203\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/team-sports-hockey/composite-sticks/junior-stick/bauer-nexus-adv-gr-stk-jr-142608.html\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"269\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/NexusADVStick/Nexus_ADV_Junior.jpg\"}}\" width=\"201\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Find Out What\'s New</strong></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Brand new for 2020 is the Bauer Nexus ADV Griptac Hockey Stick. This limited edition stick redefines stick performance. The Nexus ADV is packed with cutting edge technology to provide elite players with enhanced power and control, while remaining the lightest Nexus stick that\'s ever been created.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/team-sports-hockey/composite-sticks/senior-stick/bauer-nexus-adv-gr-stk-sr-142613.html\"><span><span><img alt=\"\" height=\"474\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/NexusADVStick/LOgo.jpg\"}}\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" width=\"738\" /></span></span></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">New Blade</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">The SlingTech Blade featured on the Bauer Nexus ADV brings new technology to the game. It features a hole along the center of the blade to create two separate areas of the blade that have different properties. By using a more rigid top of the blade for stability and control, and a flexible bottom for power, the Nexus ADV&rsquo;s SlingTech blade combines and improves two of the most important aspects of the blade. Additionally, Bauer has done extensive testing to ensure durability wouldn&rsquo;t suffer for improved performance - they have reinforced the walls around the hole for extra strength.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/team-sports-hockey/composite-sticks/senior-stick/bauer-nexus-adv-gr-stk-sr-142613.html\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"378\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/NexusADVStick/IMG_3426.JPG\"}}\" width=\"518\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/team-sports-hockey/composite-sticks/senior-stick/bauer-nexus-adv-gr-stk-sr-142613.html\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"378\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/NexusADVStick/SlingTech.jpg\"}}\" width=\"283\" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Redesigned Shaft&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">The Nexus ADV hockey stick uses a 5-sided shaft geometry that features a concave wall on the front of the stick and a concave 2-sided back wall. This shaft uses Advanced Carbon Layering with ER Spine Tech, where excess layers of carbon fibre are removed from key loading points of the stick without altering the Nexus mid-kick point.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/team-sports-hockey/composite-sticks/senior-stick/bauer-nexus-adv-gr-stk-sr-142613.html\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"781\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/NexusADVStick/IMG_3428.JPG\"}}\" width=\"880\" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Taper</span></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">The Bauer Nexus ADV features Sonic Taper Technology, which reduces weight, improves stability, and creates an energy transfer down through the stick for a faster and more powerful release. An optimized flex profile also allows you to lean much easier into the shots and achieve maximum release velocity on every type of shot.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/team-sports-hockey/composite-sticks/senior-stick/bauer-nexus-adv-gr-stk-sr-142613.html\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"459\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/NexusADVStick/IMG_3427.JPG\"}}\" width=\"893\" /></a>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">If you are an elite player, look no further than the Bauer Nexus ADV Hockey Stick for the newest technology and top-notch performance.</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/team-sports-hockey/composite-sticks/senior-stick/bauer-nexus-adv-gr-stk-sr-142613.html\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"531\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/NexusADVStick/IMG_3422.JPG\"}}\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" width=\"572\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/team-sports-hockey/composite-sticks/senior-stick/bauer-nexus-adv-gr-stk-sr-142613.html\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"362\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/NexusADVStick/IMG_3429.JPG\"}}\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" width=\"543\" /></a><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/team-sports-hockey/composite-sticks/senior-stick/bauer-nexus-adv-gr-stk-sr-142613.html\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"513\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/NexusADVStick/IMG_3421.JPG\"}}\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" width=\"622\" /></a></p>\r\n<p></p>', '2020-01-22 22:56:57', '2020-01-28 21:15:34', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
