(36, 'Vibra Fit Coach Trainer', '1column', NULL, NULL, 'vibra-fit', 'Vibra Fit Vibration Trainer', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">{{widget type=\"Magento\\\\Catalog\\\\Block\\\\Product\\\\Widget\\\\Link\" anchor_text=\"Click Here To View/Order Product\" template=\"product/widget/link/link_block.phtml\" id_path=\"product/144840\"}}</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Let the machine do the work for you! Vibra Fit Coach Vibration Devices now available in limited quantity for the best price around!</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Only $159.99 !</span></h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Retail $799.99</span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">FREE Curbside Delivery In Kitchener-Waterloo</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">As Seen On The Shopping Channel</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/vibra-fit-vibration-trainer-144840.html\" title=\"Click To View/Order Product\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"633\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/Vibra_workout_coach.jpg\"}}\" width=\"613\" /></span></a></p>\r\n<h1><iframe height=\"480\" src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/C1rO5C7BT+S.mp4\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" width=\"640\"></iframe></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>What it is:</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">This is a piece of exercise equipment that can help you keep fit and also help improve blood circulation.</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Who it is for:&nbsp;</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">This product is suitable for use by healthy adult (however, please refer to the cautions and disclaimers below).</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>What it does:&nbsp;</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">This machine features six tailored programs and a manual mode, with 20 different speed settings. The VibraFit Coach has a bigger surface that allows you to exercise more comfortably with a great and modern design and a roller on the front for easier transport. It also includes two sets of resistance bands to enhance your exercises, which can be attached at three different locations on the unit so you can also get a greater variety of exercises. When the detachable mast isn\'t attached, you will have a remote which will help you control the programs and speed without bending down to reach the panel. Once you select the workout you want to do (including upper body, ab blast, leg workout, full body, cardio or HIIT), the voice coach will talk you through each exercise while counting you in and also counting you down. You can also decide your own workout with up to 20 settings in manual mode. It\'s perfect for muscle building, general fitness, endurance, and muscle relaxation.</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em>Oscillating Motion:</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">The key difference between oscillation vibration and piston vibration is that with piston vibration, both legs are simultaneously moving upwards or downwards, but with oscillation vibration, one leg is moving up while the other is moving down, which can be compared to the action of a see-saw. The platform tilts from side to side over a central fulcrum, lifting one side of your body while at the same time dropping (displacing) the other side. This pattern is switched to and fro at a frequency set on the control panel.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Using a vibration machine like the VibraFit Coach may provide benefits to your normal routine, helping you to exercise in a different way. Just stand on the oscillating plate and do your basic exercises such as squats, press-ups, etc. Between 40 and 60 percent of a muscle\'s fibres are recruited to perform free-weight or resistance-machine exercising, but when performing similar exercises on a vibration plate, as with the Vibra Fit Coach, almost 100% of the target muscle fibres are used. This is achieved by creating an almost constant state of reflex in the muscles, known as a tonic stretch/reflex&mdash;this means that the muscles are flexing and contracting at a very high frequency, producing faster increases in muscular strength.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Oscillating motion rather than solely a vertical vibration</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Get an intense workout in only 10 minutes</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Touchscreen monitor</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Unique voice coach</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Calorie counter</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Pulse sensor</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Built-in programs&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Maximum user weight: 120 kg</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>What is included:</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; VibraFit Coach</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Touchscreen Display</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Handlebars with Pulse Sensors</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Remote Control</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; (2) Resistance Bands</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; Power Cord</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&bull; User Manual</span></p>', '2020-04-10 01:43:06', '2020-04-11 05:02:28', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(37, 'Sublimated Masks', '1column', NULL, NULL, 'sublimated-masks', 'New Protective Masks Now Available', '<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Following the CDC\'s recent recommendation that everyone should wear a fabric face cover in public setting, we have designed and are offering assorted non medical muli-use washable masks to help combat Covid-19.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Our hope is that this will allow Medical PPE to be dedicated to front line workers and provide the broader population with protection, while showing fan support to the team or sport you love and miss.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>Styles of team and brand masks available for pre-order</strong>&nbsp;.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>Select from the 5 available mask options below to browse different styles</strong></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>If you have any questions contact Vince, 519-241-4536, or email&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@sportszonecanada.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@sportszonecanada.com</a></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/bauer-non-medical-mask-144951.html\" target=\"_self\"><img height=\"441\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/Masks/bauermasks.jpg\"}}\" width=\"242\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/2ply-non-medical-sub-mask-146282.html\" title=\"Click To View\" target=\"_self\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/SALES_PROMOTIONS/Adult_team.jpg\"}}\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/2ply-non-medical-mask-custom-146280.html\" title=\"Click To View\" target=\"_self\"><img height=\"432\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/SALES_PROMOTIONS/Adult_custom.jpg\"}}\" width=\"226\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/kids-non-medical-masks-145007.html\" title=\"Click To View\" target=\"_self\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/SALES_PROMOTIONS/kids_team.jpg\"}}\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/kids-non-medical-masks-cus-145023.html\" title=\"Click To View\" target=\"_self\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/SALES_PROMOTIONS/Kids_custom.jpg\"}}\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/gaiter-style-face-cover-147945.html\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/SALES_PROMOTIONS/Gaiters.jpg\"}}\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>', '2020-05-03 20:33:52', '2020-09-02 15:51:20', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(38, 'Covid-19 Reopening At Limited Capacity', '1column', NULL, NULL, 'covid-reopening', 'Update On Covid-19 Reopening At Limited Capacity', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">In-Store Shopping Information</span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img height=\"135\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/Blog/sz.se_logo.jpg\"}}\" width=\"394\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-large; color: #000000;\">Our shop is now officially operating under <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/hours/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\">reduced hours</span></a></span></span> and limited capacity. Shopping appointments are available but not neccessary, and can be reserved using the side toolbar on our website - drop by customers will still be allowed into the store. Wearing a mask inside while shopping is not required but is encouraged as it is a primary peice of protective equipment involved in reducing the spread of COVID-19 and keeping the store environment safe.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Contactless Equipment Sizing Technology</span></h1>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Cutting edge technologies from Bauer such as the 3D Skate Scanner, and Myfit App allow us to find the sizes and models of equipment accurately in a contactless manor. These programs are tools in our shop that scan exact measurements of the body from a safe distance in order to provide accurate information for sizing.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img height=\"476\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/Blog/3d_ScaNNER.JPG\"}}\" width=\"474\" /><img height=\"340\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/Blog/bauermyfittapp.png\"}}\" width=\"645\" /></span></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Social Distanced Protective Equipment</span></h1>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">We have made changes to our store to help promote safety rules and help prevent the spread of COVID-19. Plexi glass bariers are found around front cash desks, customer service desks, and our service department to reduce risks throughout close contact processes of shopping. Also, floor stickers ensure customers shopping in-store are staying the recommended 6-foot minimum distance away from eachother.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img height=\"464\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/Masks/IMG_2130.jpg\"}}\" width=\"502\" /><img height=\"466\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/Masks/IMG_2131.jpg\"}}\" width=\"496\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">How About Trying On Equipment?</span></h1>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">In terms of customers coming in direct contact with equipment when trying it on, we take many precautions to enforce safety. Customers must sanitize with the provided bottle of sanitizer at the front doors, and wear protective glovewear (provided) when trying on any equipment like hockey gloves or baseball gloves. Any piece of equipment worn by a customer tha is not purchased will be set aside off the main floor for 48 hours.</span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/Masks/sanitizer.jpeg\"}}\" /><img height=\"352\" src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/Masks/gloves.jpg\"}}\" width=\"406\" /></h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h1>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Protective Masks</span></h1>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Our staff members are wearing protective masks in order to keep themselves and customers safe. These masks help promote clean air during your Sports Zone shopping experience. Custom masks like these are also available in store and online.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.sportszonecanada.com/sublimated-masks\" title=\"Click To View\" target=\"_self\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/Masks/SPORTSZONE_MASK.jpg\"}}\" style=\"font-size: xx-large; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" /></a></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&nbsp;</span></h1>', '2020-06-04 00:12:04', '2020-06-04 01:37:07', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
